" --- General Settings ---
colorscheme system
" --- Keybindings: jkl; movement ---
" 1. Preserve extended hint modes by moving them to 'h'
keymap h ;

" 2. Shift the lowercase movement keys one position to the right
keymap j h
keymap k j
keymap l k
keymap ; l

" 3. Shift the uppercase keys for tab navigation
bind J tabnext
bind K tabprev

" Unbind / so Zen can handle it natively for Find in Page
unbind /

" 4. History Navigation (LazyVim style)
bind <C-o> back
bind <C-i> forward

" 5. Edge Scrolling
bind zj scrollpx -9999 0
bind z; scrollpx 9999 0


" --- Search Engines ---
" Format: set searchurls.<alias> <url_with_%s>
set searchurls.w https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s
set searchurls.g https://www.google.com/search?q=%s
set searchurls.y https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s
set searchurls.gm https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s
set searchurls.az https://www.amazon.de/s/?field-keywords=%s
set searchurls.gi https://www.google.com/search?tbm=isch&q=%s
set searchurls.gd https://drive.google.com/drive/search?q=%s
set searchurls.gh https://www.github.com/search?q=%s
set searchurls.i http://www.imdb.com/find?s=all&q=%s

" --- Exclusions ---
" Automatically disable Tridactyl on these sites
blacklistadd mail.google.com
blacklistadd vim-hero.com

" --- Search & Hints ---
" Use left-hand keys for hints to avoid conflicts with our jkl; keymaps on the right hand!
set hintchars sadfqewcxz

" --- External Editor ---
" Spawn a fish shell, run Neovim, and then refocus Zen Browser when Neovim closes!
set editorcmd open -W -n -a Ghostty --args -e /opt/homebrew/bin/fish -lc 'nvim "%f"; open -a Zen'
